columns.name: name
columns.description: The name of the private endpoint.

columns.name: id
columns.description: The ID of the private endpoint.

columns.name: etag
columns.description: A unique read-only string that changes whenever the resource is updated.

columns.name: type
columns.description: The type of the private endpoint.

columns.name: provisioning_state
columns.description: The provisioning state of the private endpoint resource.

columns.name: custom_network_interface_name
columns.description: The custom name of the network interface attached to the private endpoint.

columns.name: location
columns.description: The location of the private endpoint.

columns.name: extended_location
columns.description: The extended location of the private endpoint.

columns.name: subnet
columns.description: The ID of the subnet from which the private IP will be allocated.

columns.name: network_interfaces
columns.description: An array of references to the network interfaces created for this private endpoint.

columns.name: private_link_service_connections
columns.description: A grouping of information about the connection to the remote resource.

columns.name: manual_private_link_service_connections
columns.description: A grouping of information about the connection to the remote resource. Used when the network admin does not have access to approve connections to the remote resource.

columns.name: custom_dns_configs
columns.description: An array of custom DNS configurations.

columns.name: application_security_groups
columns.description: Application security groups in which the private endpoint IP configuration is included.

columns.name: ip_configurations
columns.description: A list of IP configurations of the private endpoint.

columns.name: region
columns.description: The Azure region where the resource is located.

columns.name: resource_group
columns.description: The resource group in which the resource is located.
